Comment: In this game, Black employs an odd opening, and I am forced to show why 2...h6 is an obscure line...

A very odd line.  Black is trying to take me out of my opening repertoire, but there is a reason that no one plays this line.  2...h6 neglects the center, so I develop classically, which I feel is the best way to meet out-of-book moves.
